You can also switch to another PHP version by providing the ENV variable.

```ruby
# quick run with latest PHP and Shuwei
$ docker run --rm -p 80:80 58shuwei/{{ orca.image }}:{{ orca.tag }}

# use another php version
$ docker run --rm -p 80:80 --env PHP_VERSION=7.2 58shuwei/{{ orca.image }}:{{ orca.tag }}
```